WEBVTT

00:00:15.724 --> 00:00:16.808
I feel uneasy.

00:00:17.559 --> 00:00:19.936
Boy, this place is huge.

00:00:20.020 --> 00:00:21.855
Ugh, what is this place?

00:00:21.938 --> 00:00:25.483
It's so dark and damp.
This place is definitely bad news.

00:00:25.567 --> 00:00:29.029
I already knew the Monster Association's
hideout was bad news,

00:00:29.112 --> 00:00:31.448
but this is way creepier than I imagined.

00:00:31.531 --> 00:00:33.408
Feels like a monster could attack
at any moment.

00:00:33.491 --> 00:00:34.451
Hey, King.

00:00:34.534 --> 00:00:35.368
RUMBLE RUMBLE

00:00:35.452 --> 00:00:37.454
Saitama, where are you?!

00:00:37.537 --> 00:00:39.664
- Are you listening to me, King?
- Huh?

00:00:39.748 --> 00:00:41.791
Even for someone who's grown too strong,

00:00:41.875 --> 00:00:46.296
does a dangerous place like this
still get your blood pumping?

00:00:46.379 --> 00:00:48.047
Too strong?
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:00:48.131 --> 00:00:50.800
I doubt that.
There's always someone stronger than you.

00:00:50.884 --> 00:00:55.055
Hmm... for the strongest man on Earth,
that's a surprisingly dull thing to say.

00:00:56.014 --> 00:00:58.808
Is it so selfish to hope
that might be true?

00:00:58.892 --> 00:01:03.229
As expected.
That's how a true warrior should be.

00:01:03.313 --> 00:01:05.065
I ought to learn from you.

00:01:10.528 --> 00:01:12.697
I DON'T CONSIDER MYSELF A HERO
TRAINING? NOT FOR ME (LOL)

00:01:12.781 --> 00:01:14.866
TRYING TO CHALLENGE ME?
WARNING: DON'T DO IT

00:01:14.949 --> 00:01:16.910
TOO STRONG? I DOUBT THAT

00:01:17.535 --> 00:01:20.747
Yeah... Well, I'm not lying...

00:01:21.372 --> 00:01:24.209
We should split up
into two groups from here.

00:01:24.292 --> 00:01:25.585
Right, King?

00:01:25.668 --> 00:01:27.712
Uh, um... yeah.

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:33.760
Oh. These guys look like they live here.

00:01:34.302 --> 00:01:35.136
Hey...

00:01:37.096 --> 00:01:41.935
CRASH CRASH CRASH

00:03:12.066 --> 00:03:12.942
ULTIMATE LIFEFORM

00:03:13.026 --> 00:03:15.695
This chunk of meat...
If we attacked it together,

00:03:15.778 --> 00:03:16.613
CHOMP CHOMP
CRACK CRUNCH

00:03:16.696 --> 00:03:18.156
I thought he would be
a hearty meal for us...

00:03:18.239 --> 00:03:21.159
But he ate everybody!

00:03:23.244 --> 00:03:24.621
What the heck are you?

00:03:24.704 --> 00:03:25.663
You're just a human...

00:03:25.747 --> 00:03:29.125
Stop! Don't eat me. Nooo!

00:03:33.171 --> 00:03:35.256
THREAT LEVEL: DRAGON
GUMS

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:58.071
Why aren't you moving?

00:03:58.154 --> 00:03:59.489
Have you given up?

00:04:00.907 --> 00:04:02.492
What's going on?

00:04:03.117 --> 00:04:06.955
Superalloy Blackluster.
Why are you not fighting back?

00:04:07.038 --> 00:04:08.748
Insect God.

00:04:09.249 --> 00:04:11.751
When we first met, you told me that...

00:04:12.418 --> 00:04:16.256
You're an invincible monster
that embodies the power of insects.

00:04:16.923 --> 00:04:19.342
That is exactly
what I've been striving for.

00:04:19.425 --> 00:04:21.427
The ultimate form of insect strength!

00:04:22.553 --> 00:04:24.555
Their tough exoskeletons and

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:28.017
their perfectly efficient bodies
are impressive...

00:04:28.518 --> 00:04:32.855
But the real marvel is that
they're almost entirely made of muscle.

00:04:33.398 --> 00:04:35.858
And those muscles barely tire

00:04:35.942 --> 00:04:39.028
allowing them to stay active
for long periods.

00:04:39.112 --> 00:04:41.823
That is the perfection I aim for!

00:04:42.407 --> 00:04:46.286
I was deeply disappointed that
a monster attained it before I did.

00:04:46.369 --> 00:04:48.746
But at the same time,
I wanted to experience it for myself.

00:04:48.830 --> 00:04:51.165
The power worthy of being
called the Insect God...

00:04:51.249 --> 00:04:54.502
That speed... that terrifying strength...

00:04:55.211 --> 00:04:56.045
But...

00:04:56.129 --> 00:04:59.299
You're far less impressive
than I expected.

00:04:59.841 --> 00:05:02.051
And for a so-called insect monster,

00:05:02.135 --> 00:05:03.845
you lack the black sheen.

00:05:03.928 --> 00:05:05.013
What a letdown...

00:05:05.096 --> 00:05:06.264
What did you say?

00:05:06.347 --> 00:05:09.559
If you think you've grasped my true power,
you're gravely mistaken--

00:05:09.642 --> 00:05:10.893
What a letdown!

00:05:10.977 --> 00:05:12.145
STARTLED

00:05:12.228 --> 00:05:16.691
This body is nothing more
than oversized muscle.

00:05:16.774 --> 00:05:20.945
But its performance surpasses yours,
Insect God.

00:05:21.487 --> 00:05:23.656
And let me warn you.

00:05:23.740 --> 00:05:28.077
There are three heroes
you must never anger.

00:05:28.161 --> 00:05:30.830
The strongest creature on Earth, King.

00:05:31.331 --> 00:05:33.750
If you make him angry,
the King Engine will roar,

00:05:33.833 --> 00:05:36.335
and all evil will be wiped out.

00:05:36.419 --> 00:05:40.173
Then there's Tornado,
the psychic capable of untold slaughter!

00:05:40.673 --> 00:05:44.302
Tick her off, and she'll pulverize you
beyond recognition.

00:05:44.385 --> 00:05:45.928
Finally, there's me.

00:05:46.012 --> 00:05:49.807
Superalloy Blackluster,
always gleaming with a dark shine.

00:05:49.891 --> 00:05:50.850
Push me too far,

00:05:50.933 --> 00:05:53.478
and these muscles start
acting on their own.

00:05:53.561 --> 00:05:54.729
I see...

00:05:54.812 --> 00:05:58.107
You want to know what happens
if you anger me?

00:05:58.191 --> 00:06:01.652
Even the fists of Garou, the Hero Hunter

00:06:01.736 --> 00:06:05.740
who you've all been struggling
to defeat, had no effect on me.

00:06:05.823 --> 00:06:08.701
My outer shell is an impenetrable armor.

00:06:09.285 --> 00:06:13.664
The explosive power of insect muscles is

00:06:13.748 --> 00:06:17.627
on a whole different level
from you mammals.

00:06:17.710 --> 00:06:21.047
In other words, my whole body is a weapon.

00:06:21.130 --> 00:06:22.965
I'm going to shred those fake muscles

00:06:23.049 --> 00:06:25.885
and feed them to the bugs.

00:06:26.385 --> 00:06:28.346
That's reckless.

00:06:35.645 --> 00:06:38.022
I'll smash you to bits!

00:06:39.357 --> 00:06:42.235
I told you, that's reckless.

00:06:42.318 --> 00:06:47.198
Even I don't know how to
inflict a wound on this body.

00:06:47.740 --> 00:06:48.741
Hmm.

00:06:48.825 --> 00:06:53.704
Unless it's a top-tier monster,
my muscles don't get fired up.

00:06:54.664 --> 00:06:57.250
Whoa. The ground is shaking hard.

00:06:57.333 --> 00:06:59.544
Is someone fighting one of the big shots?

00:07:05.550 --> 00:07:07.969
Wow! That's a huge dog!

00:07:11.055 --> 00:07:11.889
Oh, I know!

00:07:14.016 --> 00:07:15.935
Here you go, doggy.

00:07:16.018 --> 00:07:17.270
I'll give you this bone,

00:07:17.353 --> 00:07:22.108
so take me to the big monster
that's making all this noise.

00:07:22.191 --> 00:07:24.735
There, there. Good doggy.

00:07:28.364 --> 00:07:31.659
Firing at me without warning?
You need to be taught some discipline.

00:07:34.412 --> 00:07:37.331
So you're one of the monsters
making all this noise?

00:07:39.667 --> 00:07:40.543
Sit.

00:08:17.830 --> 00:08:21.751
Assault team, are you okay?
Respond! What happened?

00:08:21.834 --> 00:08:23.461
Damn it. I can't tell what's going on.

00:08:26.672 --> 00:08:29.050
Earthquake...?
No, a shock wave...?

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:31.928
No high-energy reactions
detected in the vicinity...

00:08:32.512 --> 00:08:34.722
A shockwave from outside
the detection range.

00:08:34.805 --> 00:08:36.265
Its power is off the charts.

00:08:37.016 --> 00:08:39.644
Which means...
that just now was possibly...

00:08:40.436 --> 00:08:43.022
Knowing how steadfast Master Saitama is,

00:08:43.105 --> 00:08:46.108
I wouldn't be surprised if
he's already on his way to the hideout.

00:08:47.652 --> 00:08:50.696
No way... He took down Pochi
with just one punch...?

00:08:50.780 --> 00:08:52.990
He still hasn't noticed me.

00:08:53.074 --> 00:08:55.201
This is my chance to catch him off guard.

00:08:56.744 --> 00:08:58.621
Intense Catstigation!

00:08:58.704 --> 00:08:59.664
Hm?

00:09:02.917 --> 00:09:04.544
First a dog, now a cat?

00:09:04.627 --> 00:09:06.337
My claws! They didn't work!

00:09:06.420 --> 00:09:08.714
This guy is bad news.

00:09:08.798 --> 00:09:12.051
There's no reason to risk my life
for the Monster Association.

00:09:12.134 --> 00:09:13.511
I'm outta here, meow!

00:09:14.095 --> 00:09:14.929
Huh?

00:09:15.930 --> 00:09:17.431
What's his deal?

00:09:18.307 --> 00:09:20.977
Oh well, whatever.
Guess I'll get going.

00:09:21.060 --> 00:09:23.020
That was loud.

00:09:23.521 --> 00:09:27.024
Sounds like Pochi's gone quiet up there.

00:09:28.609 --> 00:09:29.694
Don't tell me...

00:09:29.777 --> 00:09:31.862
Getting worried?

00:09:31.946 --> 00:09:34.407
Maybe one of your top monsters
got taken out.

00:09:36.284 --> 00:09:38.619
So... are you the boss?

00:09:38.703 --> 00:09:43.457
Well, well... I'm delighted
you've come all the way here.

00:09:43.541 --> 00:09:46.210
Welcome to our hideout, Hero...

00:09:55.761 --> 00:10:00.683
I figured you were the one
I'd have to deal with personally...

00:10:01.601 --> 00:10:06.063
Terrible Tornado.
The prodigy of supernatural powers.

00:10:07.732 --> 00:10:09.984
My name is Gyoro-Gyoro.

00:10:10.067 --> 00:10:12.320
I am the strategist
of the Monster Association.

00:10:12.403 --> 00:10:16.616
And the creator of the new world
ruled by monsters.

00:10:16.699 --> 00:10:20.328
So basically, you're the boss here, right?

00:10:20.911 --> 00:10:21.787
Die.

00:10:56.739 --> 00:10:58.532
Is that all you got?

00:11:07.041 --> 00:11:09.210
She broke through my barrier?!

00:11:09.293 --> 00:11:12.254
Damn it... This could get ugly.

00:11:12.755 --> 00:11:16.425
Very well. I won't hold back either.

00:11:16.509 --> 00:11:18.677
I'll fight you in my true form!

00:11:21.263 --> 00:11:25.726
Tornado! Is this your first time facing
a psychic superior than yourself?

00:11:25.810 --> 00:11:27.645
Well, have fun.

00:11:27.728 --> 00:11:29.855
Super Raging Waves of Gravity.

00:11:31.899 --> 00:11:34.235
300 times gravity!

00:11:34.318 --> 00:11:37.029
I'll flatten you like a pancake.

00:11:38.406 --> 00:11:40.074
Not bad for a high ranker.

00:11:40.157 --> 00:11:41.575
Feels pretty good.

00:11:41.659 --> 00:11:44.495
But can you apply more pressure
on my right shoulder?

00:11:44.578 --> 00:11:47.331
I recently changed my pillow
and my shoulder's stiff.

00:11:47.415 --> 00:11:50.251
Why you...!

00:11:56.715 --> 00:11:57.591
Huh?

00:12:00.010 --> 00:12:00.970
Whoa, wait.

00:12:05.516 --> 00:12:08.811
Damn woman!

00:12:08.894 --> 00:12:12.565
She's much more powerful than I expected.

00:12:13.065 --> 00:12:15.401
She's leagues above her younger sister...!

00:12:15.484 --> 00:12:17.570
Alright, I get it. You're powerful.

00:12:17.653 --> 00:12:21.574
But you didn't have to kill me
so gruesomely.

00:12:21.657 --> 00:12:24.869
You're so cruel, Terrible Tornado.

00:12:25.369 --> 00:12:27.705
You're just a lump of meat
that feels no pain.

00:12:27.788 --> 00:12:29.457
What are you talking about?

00:12:29.999 --> 00:12:31.834
Now I'm going to draw out your true form.

00:12:31.917 --> 00:12:35.546
Oh no, she saw right through me.

00:12:35.629 --> 00:12:39.300
I wasn't ready... to challenge her...

00:12:39.383 --> 00:12:42.761
In that case...
there is only one option left.

00:12:42.845 --> 00:12:47.433
Lord Orochi! Please help me.

00:12:47.516 --> 00:12:51.729
Please take this woman down! Lord Orochi!

00:12:51.812 --> 00:12:57.193
Orochi? Oh yeah,
someone did mention that name.

00:12:57.276 --> 00:13:02.490
I may be the commander,
but our boss is Monster King Orochi.

00:13:02.573 --> 00:13:04.366
Even as the one who
created this true monster,

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:07.161
I can't fathom the limits
of his boundless power.

00:13:08.662 --> 00:13:12.166
It's over for you, Tornado.

00:13:13.918 --> 00:13:14.752
Hmm?

00:13:14.835 --> 00:13:17.087
Huh...? No one's coming.

00:13:17.171 --> 00:13:19.423
Why? That's strange.

00:13:19.507 --> 00:13:24.553
I've brainwashed him
to never defy my orders.

00:13:24.637 --> 00:13:28.057
Maybe he's too busy to come save you.

00:13:28.140 --> 00:13:31.644
Maybe he's facing off
with some other hero right now.

00:13:31.727 --> 00:13:33.312
They're no match for me,

00:13:33.395 --> 00:13:35.272
but I hear the others
are pretty strong too.

00:13:35.356 --> 00:13:36.899
W-Wait.

00:13:36.982 --> 00:13:40.736
Wait just a minute. Let's calm down
and talk this over. Okay?

00:13:45.199 --> 00:13:49.286
There's an opponent so powerful
he would ignore my plight?

00:13:50.037 --> 00:13:52.373
No, that can't be.
I'm up against Tornado here!

00:13:52.915 --> 00:13:54.750
Hurry up and get over here.

00:13:54.833 --> 00:13:57.002
Where did he go?

00:14:11.517 --> 00:14:14.770
First, a couple of naked guys,
then a dog and a cat.

00:14:14.853 --> 00:14:16.605
I was wondering what's coming next...

00:14:17.356 --> 00:14:19.608
And now,
something utterly absurd shows up.

00:14:27.032 --> 00:14:29.451
I live right above here.

00:14:29.535 --> 00:14:32.288
I heard some noise, so I went out
for a walk to check it out.

00:14:33.831 --> 00:14:36.041
That shockwave from earlier...

00:14:36.750 --> 00:14:39.378
It was out of the ordinary,
so I came to see for myself.

00:14:40.212 --> 00:14:42.840
It wasn't even on the watch list.

00:14:42.923 --> 00:14:47.595
An unforeseen, formidable presence
that could pose a real threat to us...

00:14:47.678 --> 00:14:51.056
It must be destroyed now
or it could be dangerous.

00:14:52.099 --> 00:14:55.185
We? So that means you guys living here

00:14:55.269 --> 00:14:57.021
are all in the same group or something?

00:14:57.104 --> 00:15:00.274
You're out here talking about
threats and danger, but...

00:15:00.816 --> 00:15:03.402
I'm the one being attacked here.

00:15:03.485 --> 00:15:04.820
I'm just fighting back.

00:15:11.118 --> 00:15:13.078
So you're going to attack me, huh?

00:15:15.497 --> 00:15:19.752
You're alive, Pochi?
Kill this human.

00:15:21.045 --> 00:15:22.504
Dang it, I got burnt!

00:15:33.265 --> 00:15:35.142
What did you do to Pochi?

00:15:35.225 --> 00:15:36.560
I punched it.

00:15:37.102 --> 00:15:39.355
How dare you burn my cape.

00:15:42.524 --> 00:15:44.902
You're definitely a monster.

00:15:44.985 --> 00:15:47.321
So I'm not holding back.
You're gonna get a normal punch.

00:15:47.404 --> 00:15:49.615
He held back against Pochi...?

00:15:49.698 --> 00:15:51.992
No, that wasn't a bluff.

00:15:52.076 --> 00:15:55.746
The monster cells within me are roaring.

00:15:56.330 --> 00:15:59.124
I see now. So it was him.

00:15:59.208 --> 00:16:01.752
That inexplicable presence I sensed...

00:16:02.336 --> 00:16:03.712
Goketsu...

00:16:03.796 --> 00:16:05.673
Centichoro...

00:16:05.756 --> 00:16:09.843
The beast rumored to live
in the ghost town above.

00:16:10.427 --> 00:16:14.056
Neither the Monster Association
nor I were responsible.

00:16:14.139 --> 00:16:15.641
It was this man!

00:16:17.810 --> 00:16:21.605
I haven't been this excited
in a long time.

00:16:23.315 --> 00:16:26.819
Every monster cell within me senses it.

00:16:26.902 --> 00:16:31.323
This man is the perfect sacrifice
for my resurrection.

00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:37.871
Looks like this will be
the final showdown.

00:16:41.250 --> 00:16:43.794
I'm interested in you.

00:16:43.877 --> 00:16:47.965
The peak of biological strength
a human can attain.

00:16:48.048 --> 00:16:51.135
How far can it hold up against me?

00:16:51.635 --> 00:16:53.929
I'm looking forward to this.

00:16:54.722 --> 00:16:59.768
Can you awaken my ego and emotions
that were shrouded in a haze?

00:17:00.811 --> 00:17:05.190
Through countless sacrifices,
I have become the ultimate lifeform.

00:17:05.941 --> 00:17:07.276
Under Gyoro-Gyoro,

00:17:07.359 --> 00:17:12.906
I endured endless fusion and combat
experiments with the strongest warriors.

00:17:12.990 --> 00:17:16.201
I evolved from a human
into an extraordinary monster...

00:17:16.285 --> 00:17:17.828
The ultimate being.

00:17:19.872 --> 00:17:24.585
Fate led you here as my sacrifice.

00:17:24.668 --> 00:17:28.005
Come, fight me like
it's a combat experiment

00:17:28.088 --> 00:17:30.049
and offer your body to me.

00:17:30.716 --> 00:17:34.178
For I am a god whose rebirth
was foretold in ancient times

00:17:34.261 --> 00:17:37.306
and destined to descend upon this world...

00:17:37.389 --> 00:17:39.058
- I am Oroch--
- Hey, that's enough.

00:17:39.141 --> 00:17:41.268
I'm not interested in you at all.

00:17:41.351 --> 00:17:44.396
Don't get all worked up by yourself...

00:17:44.480 --> 00:17:47.483
I'm sick of hearing introductions
like that. No offense.

00:17:48.150 --> 00:17:50.819
King of so-and-so...
Ancient weapon so-and-so...

00:17:50.903 --> 00:17:54.281
Final evolution so-and-so...
So-and-so of the entire universe...

00:17:54.364 --> 00:17:56.033
Blah blah blah.

00:17:56.784 --> 00:17:59.953
I've dealt with plenty like you before.

00:18:00.037 --> 00:18:01.789
So what makes you different from them?

00:18:02.664 --> 00:18:04.666
Even if you call yourself
the ultimate being...

00:18:04.750 --> 00:18:06.460
You're still going down
in one punch anyway.

00:18:08.337 --> 00:18:09.838
Guess you were just bored.

00:18:10.798 --> 00:18:12.758
You got stronger,

00:18:12.841 --> 00:18:15.219
but you got that confused
with reaching your goal.

00:18:15.844 --> 00:18:19.139
Bring it on.
But I'm not expecting much.

00:18:19.223 --> 00:18:22.601
I am destined to become a god!

00:18:45.040 --> 00:18:48.919
So in a monster hideout,
lightning can come up from underground?

00:18:49.002 --> 00:18:50.879
ZAP

00:19:38.677 --> 00:19:41.180
What... did you just... do...?

00:19:41.263 --> 00:19:43.640
Huh...? Just a normal punch.

00:19:44.641 --> 00:19:45.601
So this is...

00:19:46.351 --> 00:19:47.477
fear.

00:21:46.054 --> 00:21:48.056
RUMBLE RUMBLE

00:21:48.140 --> 00:21:50.267
Split up into two groups, huh?

00:21:50.350 --> 00:21:53.228
In that case,
I'll follow your lead, Silverfang.

00:21:53.312 --> 00:21:56.940
All right, then you can go that way.

00:21:57.024 --> 00:21:58.108
What?

00:21:58.191 --> 00:22:00.360
That means we'll go this way.

00:22:00.444 --> 00:22:02.362
Uh-huh... Then let's go.

00:22:02.446 --> 00:22:05.699
That's not what I meant
by "follow your lead."

00:22:06.450 --> 00:22:09.536
Normally, four people should be split up
into two groups of two.

00:22:09.619 --> 00:22:10.954
That's just common sense.

00:22:11.038 --> 00:22:13.332
Why do I have to end up alone?

00:22:14.249 --> 00:22:16.126
Oh well. I'll just deal with it.

00:22:16.626 --> 00:22:19.254
Until the strong heroes
wipe out the enemy,

00:22:19.338 --> 00:22:21.465
I'll hide my presence
and stay out of sight.

00:22:23.008 --> 00:22:25.177
I'll imagine that I'm a cloud.

00:22:25.260 --> 00:22:28.513
No, that sounds too grand.
I can't relate to that.

00:22:28.597 --> 00:22:30.807
I can be a
motionless microorganism that is

00:22:30.891 --> 00:22:32.642
unseen, unnoticed,
and bothering no one.

00:22:32.726 --> 00:22:34.478
That doesn't feel right either.

00:22:34.561 --> 00:22:38.106
I'm a being that is close to nothingness
and I just float around.

00:22:38.190 --> 00:22:39.066
King?

00:22:40.275 --> 00:22:41.151
Huh?!

00:22:42.819 --> 00:22:45.614
That hostage kid...?!
Why is he in front of me?

00:22:46.782 --> 00:22:48.116
I was so scared!

00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:50.285
I've been running away
all alone this whole time.

00:22:50.368 --> 00:22:53.371
There's a monster coming
after me from that way.

00:22:53.455 --> 00:22:55.499
But now that King is here,
I'm safe, right?

00:22:55.582 --> 00:22:56.833
Can you protect me?

00:22:56.917 --> 00:22:59.836
Carry me on your back
and take me to the exit!

00:23:00.420 --> 00:23:03.256
No. Well, um...that's...uh...

00:23:04.424 --> 00:23:05.258
RUMBLE RUMBLE

00:23:05.342 --> 00:23:06.802
That sound. Is that the King Engine?

00:23:06.885 --> 00:23:09.846
Um... You don't want me.

00:23:09.930 --> 00:23:13.433
It would be wiser to find
a different hero.

00:23:14.017 --> 00:23:17.187
Even if you rely on me,
I can't be of any help.

00:23:17.270 --> 00:23:20.565
If I try to help you, you'll only end up
being disappointed.

00:23:20.649 --> 00:23:22.609
He already saw through me?

00:23:22.692 --> 00:23:24.861
But my disguise was perfect.

00:23:24.945 --> 00:23:26.613
Oh no. I'm screwed.

00:23:26.696 --> 00:23:28.281
I'm so scared. Crap.

00:23:28.365 --> 00:23:29.783
My transformation is falling apart.

00:23:35.705 --> 00:23:37.207
Huh? What happened?

00:23:37.290 --> 00:23:40.627
I'm scared. Help me, Saitama!

00:23:47.300 --> 00:23:48.343
Told you so.

00:23:48.426 --> 00:23:50.470
I ended it with just one punch again.